        {
          "message": "Add more attributes to SyncWaitTime alerting event (#1413)\n\nWe use this event to track the sync duration. It'd be nice to be able to\ngroup it by flow ID (or Aggregator Account ID) so we don't keep\noverindex on one slow sync.\n\nThis commit adds some more metadata to this event.",
